data.description: The Litchfield's single-story design showcases a flexible floor plan ideal for families. This home encompasses two baths and three or four bedrooms, as well as a formal dining room that can be converted to a private study. The traditional foyer opens to a family room, where a recessed fireplace can be added. Overlooking the family room is the kitchen and its center island/bar. The kitchen, appointed with quality-crafted cabinetry, durable countertops, and sleek appliances, opens to the breakfast nook, which opens to the lanai. The covered porch, which can be screened, also opens to the owner's suite.
